{"id":"6950e017bef7a2c2b62ed556","title":"pebble 復活","image":null,"created":1766907928,"updated":1766907931,"lines":[{"id":"6950e017bef7a2c2b62ed556","text":"pebble 復活","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99b4","text":"from [20251126] #1126","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907931},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99b5","text":"pebble 復活","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99b6","text":"[Pebble]は2016年にFitbitに買収されました。この買収は約2300万ドルで、Pebbleのソフトウェアエンジニアやテスター、知的財産権（OS、アプリ、クラウドサービス、特許など）が対象でしたが、Pebbleのハードウェアや負債は含まれていませんでした。[Fitbit]はPebbleブランドを閉鎖し、その資産を取り込む形で事業を継続しましたが、Pebbleの製品はその後生産を終了しました。そのため、PebbleはFitbitにより実質的に買収・吸収され、ブランドとしては終了しています。その後、Fitbit自体も[Google]に買収されています.[1][3][5]","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99b7","text":"","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99b8","text":"[1](https://techcrunch.com/2016/11/30/fitbit-pebble/)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99b9","text":"[2](https://maonline.jp/articles/pebble)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99ba","text":"[3](https://www.theverge.com/news/713931/pebble-smartwatch-name-trademark-recovered)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99bb","text":"[4](https://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/12386790/)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99bc","text":"[5](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pebble_(watch))","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99bd","text":"[6](https://devlife.blog.jp/archives/49185130.html)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99be","text":"[7](https://www.silicon.co.uk/mobility/tales-tech-history-pebble-smartwatch-220973/2)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99bf","text":"[8](https://tabkul.com/?p=127071)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c0","text":"[9](https://slidebean.com/story/what-happened-to-pebble-smartwatch)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c1","text":"[10](https://xtech.nikkei.com/it/atcl/news/16/120803671/)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c2","text":"","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c3","text":"元Pebbleの元CEOで創業者の[エリック・ミギコフスキー]は、PebbleをFitbitに売却した後、スタートアップアクセラレーターの[Y Combinator]のパートナーを務め、数多くのスタートアップに助言してきました。彼はメッセージングアプリ会社の[Beeper]を共同創業し、2024年にそれを[Automattic]に売却しています。その後、2025年に旧[Pebble OS]のオープンソース化をGoogleに要請し認められたことで、Pebbleの夢をもう一度実現するために新たな会社[Core Devices]を立ち上げ、Pebbleの後継とされるスマートウォッチの開発を始めました。彼の目標は利益追求ではなく持続可能な製品作りであり、少数精鋭のチームで趣味嗜好的なマーケットを狙っています.[1][2][3][4]","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c4","text":"","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c5","text":"[1](https://betakit.com/this-time-eric-migicovsky-wont-let-anything-get-in-his-way/)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c6","text":"[2](https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/27/24352968/pebble-smartwatch-open-source-google-comeback)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c7","text":"[3](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eric_Migicovsky)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c8","text":"[4](https://ericmigi.com/blog/pebble-rebble-and-a-path-forward)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99c9","text":"[5](https://ericmigi.com/blog/success-and-failure-at-pebble)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99ca","text":"[6](https://www.atomsandbits.io/p/interview-with-eric-migicovsky-founder)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99cb","text":"[7](https://www.reddit.com/r/gadgets/comments/1ibkayl/eric_migicovsky_why_were_bringing_pebble_back/)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99cc","text":"[8](https://techcrunch.com/2025/03/18/pebble-creator-unveils-the-first-new-pebble-inspired-smartwatches/)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99cd","text":"[9](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k3W1nxHHZjI)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99ce","text":"[10](https://uwaterloo.ca/systems-design-engineering/events/start-culture-and-life-entrepreneur)","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928},{"id":"6950e01700000000008f99cf","text":"","created":1766907928,"updated":1766907928}]}